== About CORS

see for example https://templth.wordpress.com/2014/11/12/understanding-and-using-cors/.

== Usage in skysail

Since 0.2.0 of skysail.server, CORS can be configured per application with a configuration file like this:

----
corsOrigins = "*"
corsAllowedHeaders = ...
corsExposedHeaders = ...
corsMethods = ...
corsAllowCredentials = ...
----
